General.Name: Amway (Malaysia) Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Amway (Malaysia) Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the distribution of consumer products under the Amway trademark in Malaysia and Brunei. It offers nutrition and wellness products, including vitamin, mineral, and dietary supplements under the Nutrilite brand; skin care and cosmetic products, such as skincare products and colour cosmetics under the ARTISTRY brand; oral care products under the GLISTER brand; body care products under the BODY SERIES brand; and hair care products under the SATINIQUE brand. The company also provides household cleaning products under the L.O.C. brand; laundry care products under the SA8 brand; water treatment systems under the eSpring brand; and air treatment systems under the Atmosphere SKY brand. The company was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia. Amway (Malaysia) Holdings Berhad is a subsidiary of GDA B.V.
